{"tid":2277323,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[本地遊] 睇芒草, 唔一定要迫大東山, 禾秧坑上禾秧山都有","createTime":"2020-11-08T11:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T00:40:00.000Z","uid":121784,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3969045f81ed52710fa1d46e0a75fe48358c445d","tid":2277323,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"城門水塘起步, 上波羅壩自然教育徑, 跨過引水道, 然後就開始來料!<br />\n左轉上賞蠂園, 然後直上龍門郊遊徑, 再續走延長段...<br />\n連綿不絕既樓梯, 1.2公里內急升250米, 都幾辛苦下<br />\n<br />\n來到400幾米高, 有個開揚位, 望到上面山頂有幾舊石, 就係一陣要上既禾秧山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DeOHaQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDeOHaQG.jpg&h=485f84db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行多四個字, 見到呢塊山洪警告牌, 其實就係禾秧坑澗口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FurCwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FurCwt.jpg&h=30f22e19&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我地見GPS偏差左少少, 於是繼續前行, 見到另一個澗口有絲帶, 於是就入去<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBcEc48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBcEc48.jpg&h=78b4be0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 越行條坑越細, 唔多對路...check下GPS原來偏離左禾秧坑, 於是搵位, 穿越密林橫移返去...<br />\n今次真係俾絲帶fake左, 浪費左我地三個字時間......<br />\n<br />\n回望穿林來路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbsMCxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbsMCxo.jpg&h=c8061129&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條路終於似樣D~<br />\n澗勢急速上陡, 每舊石都超級大舊, 爬起上來好吃力...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/329Wfjv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F329Wfjv.jpg&h=42a2aefb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到570米海拔左右, 終於有第一條長瀑, 名叫&quot;奇石瀑&quot;, 因為左邊有舊巨石, 就咁浪住係度, 好想跌落來, 但點推都唔郁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2L71rrF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2L71rrF.jpg&h=727f225a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天氣反常, 11月仲有30度, 最好就係攀下瀑, 俾山水沖下個身, 即刻涼浸浸~<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GEvjNv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GEvjNv.jpg&h=5fa64134&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無著防滑涼鞋既人, 技術無咁高既人, 就行旁邊山路上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmB2aUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmB2aUZ.jpg&h=30ff306e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有長瀑可攀, 好正~<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wX0FG1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwX0FG1N.jpg&h=da7ab47e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一連串既長瀑, 就以呢個噴霧瀑作結, 流水由瀑頂石縫, 化作小水珠噴出, 好特別~<br />\n此瀑好難正攀, 右邊有山路上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmyjXAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmyjXAz.jpg&h=8c59be1d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上到瀑頂, 已經差不多700米高, 已經開始有芒草~<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgLZdac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgLZdac.jpg&h=d7b8acd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n720米高度離澗, 穿越竹林隧道, 好彩唔刮腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0d0G3N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0d0G3N.jpg&h=95ba58e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n離開竹林後, 就會見到一大片芒草<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjQROJ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjQROJ1.jpg&h=1d7a6aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上去禾秧山頂打卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFGNm4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFGNm4b.jpg&h=3a797dd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後就落山...回望剛才的山頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OM8v4hM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOM8v4hM.jpg&h=88bb0882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落山途中, 經過石天門, 又係時候爬下~<br />\n身手好又瘦既人, 可以爬入石天門, 然後由門既另一邊捐出來<br />\n我試過, 失敗左=.=<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQKSybi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQKSybi.jpg&h=9e1caf53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩到超哂時, 之後沿山路高速爆落到圓玄學院, 結束行程"},{"pid":"958c5e2ebc36d87261b96ed87514f4f4bcb38156","tid":2277323,"uid":164477,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"知就得喇 仲唔撚夠多人咩"},{"pid":"cb528b6c41c662ced3cd47b543783b7af0e62a85","tid":2277323,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:28:58.000Z","msg":"根本周圍都係 係無腦港女先會一窩蜂去同一個地方打卡明明 大撚把世外桃園"},{"pid":"489691e48fa7e7b9cf209d83d9072574b83cb6f6","tid":2277323,"uid":146574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3969045f81ed52710fa1d46e0a75fe48358c445d","tid":2277323,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"城門水塘起步, 上波羅壩自然教育徑, 跨過引水道, 然後就開始來料!<br />\n左轉上賞蠂園, 然後直上龍門郊遊徑, 再續走延長段...<br />\n連綿不絕既樓梯, 1.2公里內急升250米, 都幾辛苦下<br />\n<br />\n來到400幾米高, 有個開揚位, 望到上面山頂有幾舊石, 就係一陣要上既禾秧山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DeOHaQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDeOHaQG.jpg&h=485f84db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行多四個字, 見到呢塊山洪警告牌, 其實就係禾秧坑澗口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FurCwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FurCwt.jpg&h=30f22e19&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我地見GPS偏差左少少, 於是繼續前行, 見到另一個澗口有絲帶, 於是就入去<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBcEc48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBcEc48.jpg&h=78b4be0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 越行條坑越細, 唔多對路...check下GPS原來偏離左禾秧坑, 於是搵位, 穿越密林橫移返去...<br />\n今次真係俾絲帶fake左, 浪費左我地三個字時間......<br />\n<br />\n回望穿林來路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbsMCxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbsMCxo.jpg&h=c8061129&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條路終於似樣D~<br />\n澗勢急速上陡, 每舊石都超級大舊, 爬起上來好吃力...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/329Wfjv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F329Wfjv.jpg&h=42a2aefb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到570米海拔左右, 終於有第一條長瀑, 名叫&quot;奇石瀑&quot;, 因