mbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F329Wfjv.jpg&h=42a2aefb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到570米海拔左右, 終於有第一條長瀑, 名叫&quot;奇石瀑&quot;, 因為左邊有舊巨石, 就咁浪住係度, 好想跌落來, 但點推都唔郁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2L71rrF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2L71rrF.jpg&h=727f225a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天氣反常, 11月仲有30度, 最好就係攀下瀑, 俾山水沖下個身, 即刻涼浸浸~<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GEvjNv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GEvjNv.jpg&h=5fa64134&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無著防滑涼鞋既人, 技術無咁高既人, 就行旁邊山路上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmB2aUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmB2aUZ.jpg&h=30ff306e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有長瀑可攀, 好正~<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wX0FG1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwX0FG1N.jpg&h=da7ab47e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一連串既長瀑, 就以呢個噴霧瀑作結, 流水由瀑頂石縫, 化作小水珠噴出, 好特別~<br />\n此瀑好難正攀, 右邊有山路上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmyjXAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmyjXAz.jpg&h=8c59be1d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上到瀑頂, 已經差不多700米高, 已經開始有芒草~<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgLZdac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgLZdac.jpg&h=d7b8acd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n720米高度離澗, 穿越竹林隧道, 好彩唔刮腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0d0G3N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0d0G3N.jpg&h=95ba58e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n離開竹林後, 就會見到一大片芒草<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjQROJ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjQROJ1.jpg&h=1d7a6aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上去禾秧山頂打卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFGNm4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFGNm4b.jpg&h=3a797dd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br